OL,3,CHomelessness on the rise in the south
OL,4,Cof Scotland
OL,6,FHomelessness is on the rise in
OL,7,Fsouthern Scotland, new figures have
OL,8,Frevealed.
OL,10,FScottish Government statistics show a
OL,11,Ffive per cent increase in Dumfries and
OL,12,FGalloway with 1,215 homelessness
OL,13,Fapplications in 2024-25 compared to
OL,14,F1,160 the year before.
OL,16,FThe Scottish Borders recorded a one
OL,17,Fper cent drop with 755 applications -
OL,18,Fdown 10 on 2023-24.
