OL,3,CHomelessness on the rise in the south
OL,4,Cof Scotland
OL,6,FCitizens Advice Scotland, CAS, housing
OL,7,Fspokesperson Aoife Deery said: "These
OL,8,Fnew figures show without doubt the
OL,9,Fdeepening nature of the national
OL,10,Fhousing emergency with over 17,000
OL,11,Fhouseholds in temporary accommodation
OL,12,Flast year, an increase of 6%.
OL,14,F"Demand for housing advice from our
OL,15,Fadvisers in bureaux across Scotland is
OL,16,Falso growing, which highlights the
OL,17,Fvalue of advice as people face
OL,18,Funimaginable uncertainty about their
OL,19,Fhomes.
